arabic.title: الواد السمارة
text: ده انا لسى يا دوب بناديه
ده انا لسى يا دوب بناديه

english.title: The Dark-Skinned Boy
text: Can you, handsome, even once stop
Going away from me and missing me
Do you want to run away from me, handsome,
Given that we are in love?
Do you think that your heart gave up on me
Meaning it is able to go away and not come
You are part of me and being away from you
Of course won’t set me free
Wake up, boy, I’m telling you I fell in love
It looks like he went crazy
So what is the deal, the deal?
As if he wanted to forget me
He doesn’t want to come back to me
If he can deal with us not talking
It’s just a matter of two minutes
And he will come back here again
You would like to come back to me
But you are aloof towards me
You think you are able to beat
Because you are naive and don’t know me
Twice, three, or one hundred times
It looks like you fell for me
Advise your heart and tell it
That it would be better to win me and not lose me
It looks like he went crazy
So what is the deal, the deal?
As if he wanted to forget me
He doesn’t want to come back to me
If he can deal with us not talking
It’s just a matter of two minutes
And he will come back here again

arabic.title: هيحصل ايه
text: نفسي اصدق كلامك مش عارقه ليه خايفة كده
هو حبيبي اللي بينا حاجات كتير فوق كل ده
انا بحبك وعارفة ما قدرش اعيش من غير هواك
كل ما ببعد ثواني برجع قوام نفسي في لقاك
عينيّ تشوفك تسلم وتقول خلاص هفضل معاك

english.title: What Will Happen
text: I want to believe what you are saying, I don’t know why I am so afraid
Moreover, my love, we have so much together
Because what I saw in my life
Made me afraid of this and that
I don't know why I am like this
If I told you, my love
That I saw in your love
That there is no one other than you, my darling
If I told you, my love
That I saw in your love
That there is no one other than you, my darling
I love you and I know that I can't live without your love
Every time I go away even for a few seconds, I come back immediately, wanting to meet you
My eyes greet you and say that’s it, I’ll stay with you
If I told you, my love
That I saw in your love
That there is no one other than you, my darling
If I told you, my love
That I saw in your love
That there is no one other than you, my darling
